dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows topography and places of historical interest.
Features 2 pictorial vignettes: Convent de Ste. Catherine -- Chasse Ste. Catherine.
Illustrations of men, camels, and settlements.
"195" -- top right corner. "N. ij" -- bottom right corner.
Appears in Mallet's Beschreibung des gantzen Welt-Kreisses. Frankfurt/Main : 1684-5. Bd. II Fig. LXXXV.
